<figureCitation box="[151,276,369,395]" captionStart="FIGURES 30–33" captionStartId="18.[151,264,1866,1891]" captionTargetBox="[164,1424,389,1829]" captionTargetId="figure@18.[151,1436,381,1841]" captionTargetPageId="18" captionText="FIGURES 30–33. Male morphology of Porricondyla bidentula (30–31) and Porricondyla diversicornis (32–33), holotypes. 30: Fourth flagellomere, lateral. 31: Genitalia, ventral. 32: Genitalia, ventral. 33: Fourth flagellomere, lateral. Scales 0.05 mm. Arrows refer to characters described in the diagnoses." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3621097" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3621097/files/figure.png" pageId="17" pageNumber="168">Figs 30–31</figureCitation>
